show.description: Ning Xiaoyao pursues a fragment of an outer god's soul to the mortal realm, saving Zhong Qing and aiding her family. Misunderstood by the Bai family and his former fiancée, Bai Zhiqiu, he uncovers a traitor within their ranks. After slaying the outer god, the Bai family realizes his true status and regrets their past disrespect.
